### Simple GET request
GET https://httpbin.org/get

###

### GET with query parameters
GET https://httpbin.org/get?name=John&age=30

###

### GET with headers
GET https://httpbin.org/headers
User-Agent: POSTPER/1.0
Accept: application/json
X-Custom-Header: CustomValue

