### POST with JSON body
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "age": 25,
  "active": true
}

###

### PUT request
PUT https://httpbin.org/put
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 123,
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "status": "modified"
}

###

### DELETE request
DELETE https://httpbin.org/delete

###

### PATCH request
PATCH https://httpbin.org/patch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active"
}

